--- !u!114 &1519548518
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1519548514}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0e09f156ea27649c8a89ed219d2e6635, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueTrigger
  dialogue:
    sentences:
    - "*Hrmph*...\t"
    - 'My wife, Music Cat, is upset about losing her family heirloom. I wish I could
      cheer her up. '
    - What do you want?
    - Info?
    - 'I don''t usually talk to cops, but tell you what. '
    - You see that patron over there? Hasn't paid his tab. But I know he has the
      cash. It's sitting out over there!
    - 'You "help" him pay his tab, and I''ll tell you what I know. '
    startQuestId: bar_quest
    completeQuestId: 
    requiredItem: 
    fallbackDialogue: 
  questDialogue:
    sentences:
    - Patron still owes me...
    startQuestId: 
    completeQuestId: 
    requiredItem: 
    fallbackDialogue: 
  rewardDialogue:
    sentences:
    - Well that settles that. Thanks.
    - 'All I know about Fluffy is that he''s cheap. Only ever gets the house stuff. '
    - I don't get it, he's a famous journalist!
    - Why would a famous journalist stay here when there are way nicer places in
      the area?
    - 'Yeah. This isn''t his first stay. He comes through every once in a while. '
    - 'That''s all I know. I didn''t see anything last night. '
    startQuestId: 
    completeQuestId: bar_quest
    requiredItem: 
    fallbackDialogue: 
  completedDialogue:
    sentences:
    - 'I''ve already told you everything I know. '
    startQuestId: 
    completeQuestId: 
    requiredItem: 
    fallbackDialogue: 
  requiredItem: moneyRoll
  requiredItems: []
  questId: bar_quest
