  dialogue:
    sentences:
    - Welcome to the Cat Nap!
    - Thank you for coming in to investigate. Your room is almost ready. In the meantime,
      enjoy the lobby!!
    - 'It sure is a shame about Mr. Fluffy''s disappearance. We discovered his room
      was thrashed during turn-down service. '
    - 'He was a very kind patron. He''s stayed with us a couple times. '
    startQuestId: next_level
    completeQuestId: 
